FBIS4-55719 "dreeu098_k_94002" FBIS-EEU-94-098 Daily Report 11 May 1994 CROATIA Ex-Yugoslav Army Officer To Advise Martic Ex-Yugoslav Army Officer To Advise Martic AU1905152894 Belgrade BORBA in Serbo-Croatian 11 May 94 p 4 AU1905152894 Belgrade BORBA Serbo-Croatian BFN [BETA attributed report: "General Domazetovic -- Special Adviser to Martic"] [Text] Knin -- At its session yesterday, the supreme defense command of the republic of Serbian Krajina appointed Colonel-General Ljubomir Domazetovic as special defense adviser to the supreme commander and president of the republic of Serbian Krajina, Milan Martic. Colonel-General Ljubomir Domazetovic was a prominent, high-ranking officer in the Yugoslav Army until he was retired in the summer of 1993.
